query:
-- Ver sesiones CAELION activas
SELECT 
  id,
  sessionId,
  userId,
  caelionEnabled,
  currentRLD,
  totalInteractions,
  status,
  startedAt,
  completedAt
FROM caelionSessions
ORDER BY startedAt DESC
LIMIT 5;
